snippet.title: Nixie Dev Log | My First Experience with Unity
snippet.description:
Alternate title: I actually finished a Unity tutorial series.

Anyway, I'm attempting to make a video game about a robot named Nixie. I have no idea how long it will take or what I am doing, but now I have slightly more idea of what I'm doing. Hope you follow my progress!

Follow Nixie!
Website - nixiegame.com
Twitter - @pinwizkid
Instagram - @superbaileygram
Facebook - facebook.com/Nixiegamedev
Discord invite - https://discord.com/invite/s5E8PPD4Vv

Tutorial Series Link:
https://youtu.be/rMr1sHQ0_bc

Assets:
